  "summary": "This proposal defines an external API of an extensible Forwarder whose responsibility is to validate transaction signatures on-chain and expose the signer to the destination contract, that is expected to accommodate all use-cases. The ERC-712 structure of the forwarding request can be extended allowing wallets to display readable data even for types not known during the Forwarder contract deployment.",
